        <updateDate>2021-12-23T13:43:57Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Stopping Abortion Bounties Act</strong></p> <p>This bill imposes a 100% tax on amounts received as statutory damages under a state bounty statute. A<em> bounty statute</em> is a statute that authorizes a person to file a civil action and collect damages for assisting another person in exercising the right to have an abortion.</p> <p>The bill also directs the Department of the Treasury to award a grant to any person who pays or incurs amounts under a court order resulting from a suit filed under a bounty statute, including the amount paid or incurred as statutory damages and reasonable attorney's fees.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
